'''《好好》'''是[[台灣|台灣]]歌手[[李宣榕|李宣榕]]首張正規錄音室流行音樂專輯，由[[福茂唱片|福茂唱片]]公司於2020年12月10日正式發行。<ref>{{cite news |language =zh | url = https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/20201210ent023/ | title = 星光一班李宣榕雙喜臨門 見偶像林書豪祝福破涕為笑| publisher = 鏡週刊 Mirror Media-娛樂頭條| date = 2020-12-10}}</ref>且此專輯距離2017年首張音樂EP《[[李宣榕Sharon_Lee_首張同名EP|李宣榕Sharon Lee 首張同名EP]]》相隔三年。<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://stars.udn.com/star/story/10092/4522154 |title = 李宣榕母胎單身33年 戀愛卡關憶亡父噴淚 |publisher = 噓！星聞-音樂新聞 |date = 2020-04-27 |accessdate = 2021-01-22 |archive-date = 2020-08-30 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200830111435/https://stars.udn.com/star/story/10092/4522154 |dead-url = no }}</ref>

專輯首波主打歌《好好》，該音樂MV則是邀請著名男演員[[胡宇威|胡宇威]]擔任男主角<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20201206002336-260404?chdtv |title = 李宣榕與胡宇威「好好」談戀愛 肢體顛倒喝交杯 |publisher = 中時新聞網-娛樂新聞 |date = 2020-12-06 |accessdate = 2021-01-17 |archive-date = 2021-10-21 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211021174428/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20201206002336-260404?chdtv |dead-url = no }}</ref>，該曲同時也成為李宣榕所參演的[[TVBS歡樂台|TVBS歡樂台]]《[[女力報到－好運到|女力報到－好運到]]》與《[[女力報到－愛情公寓|女力報到－愛情公寓]]》電視劇片尾曲<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://news.tvbs.com.tw/entertainment/1450271 |title = 李宣榕戲劇表現亮眼　告假劇組將回歸 |publisher = TVBS NEWS-娛樂新聞 |date = 2021-01-17 |accessdate = 2021-01-22 |archive-date = 2021-02-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210204005119/https://news.tvbs.com.tw/entertainment/1450271 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/3415446 |title = 李宣榕消失《女力》3個月 錯愕分手王建復 |publisher = 自由娛樂-即時新聞 |date = 2021-01-19 |accessdate = 2021-01-22 |archive-date = 2021-01-28 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210128092451/https://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/3415446 |dead-url = no }}</ref>，專輯第二波主打歌《備忘錄詩人》，則邀請知名音樂錄影帶導演[[黃子然|黃子然]]拍攝
<ref>{{cite news |language = zh | url = https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20201224005908-260404?chdtv | 
title = 李宣榕泥巴地唱獨角戲 唯美幻想險摔踉蹌 | publisher =中時新聞網-娛樂新聞|date = 2020-12-24}}</ref>，該曲成為[[八大戲劇台|八大戲劇台]]熱播韓劇《[[一起吃晚餐嗎？|一起吃晚餐嗎？]]》片尾曲。

專輯第三波主打歌《親愛的》，則是邀請著名女演員[[梁舒涵|梁舒涵]]一起合唱，並且為該音樂MV擔任女主角。<ref>{{cite news | language = zh | url = https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=887245 | title = 「朵娥CP」合體！李宣榕曝「梁舒涵貼心之舉」：心思細膩 | publisher = 三立新聞網 SETN.COM-娛樂新聞 | date = 2021-01-24 | accessdate = 2021-02-12 | archive-date = 2021-01-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210125132433/https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=887245 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

